### ============================================================
### Presale V2 — Storefront + Cart
### Base URL: https://localhost:49609
###
### Storefront: anonymous (published products browse)
### Cart: authenticated (any user — operates on own cart via userId)
###
### Full checkout flow:
###   1. Browse products  →  GET /api/storefront/products
###   2. Add to cart      →  POST /api/v2/cart/items
###   3. View cart        →  GET  /api/v2/cart
###   4. Place order      →  POST /api/v2/orders  (see sales-orders-v2.http)
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = https://localhost:49609
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
@contentType = application/json

# ============================================================
# AUTH
# ============================================================

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@localhost",
  "password": "aDminN@W25!"
}

###

# ============================================================
# STOREFRONT — public product browse (anonymous)
# ============================================================

### Browse published products — first page
# Expected: 200 OK  →  StorefrontProductListVm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/storefront/products?pageSize=10&pageNo=1
###

### Browse published products — search
# Expected: 200 OK  →  filtered list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/storefront/products?searchString=laptop&pageSize=5&pageNo=1
###

### Browse published products — next page
# Expected: 200 OK
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/storefront/products?pageSize=5&pageNo=2
###

# ============================================================
# CART — authenticated
# ============================================================

### Get current user's cart
# Expected: 200 OK  →  CartVm  |  404 if cart is empty/doesn't exist
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Add item to cart (or update quantity if already in cart)
# Expected: 200 OK
# Replace userId with the actual user id from the JWT claim
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "8e445865-a24d-4543-a6c6-9443d048cdb9",
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}
###

### Add another item
# Expected: 200 OK
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "replace-with-real-user-id",
  "productId": 2,
  "quantity": 1
}
###

### Update quantity of existing cart item (same productId → overwrites)
# Expected: 200 OK
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/cart/items
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "8e445865-a24d-4543-a6c6-9443d048cdb9",
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 5
}
###

### Remove single item from cart
# Expected: 204 No Content
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/cart/items/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Clear entire cart
# Expected: 204 No Content
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get cart after clearing — should be empty/404
# Expected: 404 Not Found (or empty CartVm depending on implementation)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###
